main event: Two round objects, red and green, appeared to change colors and were purportedly larger than navigational lights.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about 35-40 seconds., The objects were observed moving from west to east., The local Ground Operations Center (GOC) plotted two aircraft in the area at the time., The lights suggested the possibility of aircraft., Evaluation concluded that the objects were probably aircraft.
